Import Tuner is dedicated to the true import lifestyle. Each issue offers unbeatable coverage of the hottest cars and the coolest shows with full-color photo features, complete event coverage, step-by-step guides showing you how to install aftermarket products, reviews of the latest gear, and extensive product listings. This magazine is what every import performance tuner needs to build the hottest ride.
